- Design APIs to return opaque errors to clients and avoid leaking whether an email exists during reset/resend endpoints.
- Provide UI copy variants for messages (success, error, pending verification) and microcopy for 2FA setup & recovery codes.

## Deliverables
- Frontend code: pages and components described (React+TS or Vue+TS), ready to integrate into Archject frontend.
- Backend code: auth service with endpoints, DB migrations/schema, and secrets management notes.
- Configuration & Deployment README: env vars, third-party provider setup, local dev instructions.
- OpenAPI/Swagger documentation and Postman collection.
- Test suite: unit tests and E2E test scenarios covering Acceptance Criteria.
- Design assets: Figma or style tokens mapping for colors, typography, spacing, and component states.

Implement this feature with security, reliability, and the provided visual system in mind. Prioritize clear developer documentation and testability so the authentication system can be audited and extended (SAML/SCIM, enterprise provisioning) in the future.

